{"tid":1634412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位手足，食飽飯休息完又要開工喇，今晚八點，十八區見","createTime":"2019-10-07T07:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T10:17:36.000Z","uid":12773,"like":53,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"5f3ac494717f8d683b229989cb1f570c2f607363","tid":1634412,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"今次係香港史上<br />\n最長的激進示威<br />\n係呢方面<br />\n大家都係小學生在學習之中<br />\n我知條路好長<br />\n亦可能會有謾罵與批評<br />\n但只要理念正確<br />\n我地絕不放棄<br />\n亦唔會停<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一陣十八區見</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山<br />\n各有各做<br />\n不分化<br />\n不割蓆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">勇武繼續裝修<br />\n繼續比壓力政府<br />\n和理非繼續上街，做文宣<br />\n掩護勇武手足做野<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n香港人係世上最勇敢的民族<br />\n不答應五大訴求<br />\n我們絕不會停手</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72959aa30c1894e3fa8c1ac41a45f5ee5010d78b","tid":1634412,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im